   ELITE (Firebird)

   First of all, when the game asks you to enter the password, type in
   SARA (RETURN), then the correct code.  Start the game and press the
   asterisk(*) on the NUMERIC keypad and HEY PRESTO!  The hack screen!
   Now you can change values to add items to your inventory.

